Effective Mass

We calculate the effective mass following https://arxiv.org/abs/1612.06963.

\(m^{eff}(t,\tau)=\frac{1}{\tau}ln\left(\frac{C(t)}{C(t+\tau)}\right)\rightarrow_{t\rightarrow \infty} \frac{1}{\tau}ln(e^{E_0\tau})=E_0\)
